{"tid":2250781,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被指向旺角警署投汽油彈 工人認罪候判 官質疑控方檢控基礎 ‘如非辯方同意我基本上唔會撞納’","createTime":"2020-10-20T10:36:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T16:43:55.000Z","uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"68041bfd55bf6452467021d3669ef85c61682300","tid":2250781,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T10:36:50.000Z","msg":"年輕玻璃幕牆工人被指於去年 10 月 14 日，連同他人於旺角警署外縱火，被控一項有意圖而企圖縱火罪，他今（20 日）於區域法院認罪，獲准繼續保釋至下周四進行求情。法官郭啟安一度質疑控方的檢控基礎不足以支持控罪，控方其後修訂部分案情並獲辯方同意，法官則指如非辯方接納相關修訂案情，「我基本上係唔會接納」，但現時辯方接納，「我都無嘢好講」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/court/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%90%91%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E6%8A%95%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-%E5%B7%A5%E4%BA%BA%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%AA%E5%80%99%E5%88%A4-%E5%AE%98%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E6%8E%A7%E6%96%B9%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%2590%2591%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E6%258A%2595%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588-%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E5%2580%2599%25E5%2588%25A4-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%259F%25BA%25E7%25A4%258E%2F&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEUYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=ed7a65f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%2590%2591%25E6%2597%25BA%25E8%25A7%2592%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E6%258A%2595%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588-%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E5%2580%2599%25E5%2588%25A4-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%259F%25BA%25E7%25A4%258E%2F&h=9d21f4a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/court/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%90%91%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E8%A