f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa0dac9e7349868f83168974d694aad401559670","tid":2250781,"uid":20563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T11:24:04.000Z","msg":"係咪果d 一開始就講：你認左佢啦，判輕d. 你唔認，佢都會一直上數，輸既都係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7978e69321acbe5565021338be641241a1ea55bf","tid":2250781,"uid":179718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T11:30:12.000Z","msg":"開名啦<br />\n乜撚嘢律師嚟"},{"pid":"f9c4b24279d3eefb2d87624f1fea1734353f0708","tid":2250781,"uid":55197,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T11:33:51.000Z","msg":"控方其後申請修訂案情，加入當時旺角警署內有警員辦公，側門有警員出入，亦有警員戒備。相關案情指，去年 10 月 13 日晚，有身穿黑色蒙面人士向旺角警署正門投擲多枚汽油彈 ，警方事後加強巡邏戒備。翌晨 1 時許，被告與黃現身警署側門對面，被告燃點手上的汽油彈並朝向警署側門投擲，黃亦投擲手上的汽油彈，兩枚汽油彈落在旺角警署側門外的外牆碎裂，但沒有起火，在場監視的警員則上前拘捕兩人。被告警誡下指「阿 Sir，我知錯，我承認我有掟汽油彈，我無諗過咁嚴重㗎」。<span class=\"red\">被告其後又指案發前有人致電他，對方表示有被告女友的裸照，要求被告替他做事，被告才參與犯案。</span><br />\n咁奇怪？"},{"pid":"32ecae348bf5ffd6e87c4369214f1a6c13f4ea7f","tid":2250781,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T12:28:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個律師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"265e0435d6384930aaadb15a819ed89aea66feb2","tid":2250781,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T12:33:47.000Z","msg":"法援派嗰啲？"},{"pid":"c423ca2e7b9341bd427482683f01824a77bb55fa","tid":2250781,"uid":250105,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T12:40:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"34ab09e6237f8b8985c8fd8f9ca7e5a2f1ce3773","tid":2250781,"uid":185854,"li